sequenceDiagram
  participant S as Scheduler (15 min)
  participant A as Habit Engine
  participant G as Identity Gate
  participant H as Heuristics
  participant V as VLM (rare)
  participant M as SQLite Metrics

  S->>A: tick
  A->>G: is_primary_user_present? guest_mode_off? track_me_on?
  G-->>A: yes/no

  alt gated off
    A-->>M: no update (or "skipped" count)
  else gated on
    A->>H: cheap checks (change-detection)
    H-->>A: confident state OR uncertain

    alt uncertain or state-changed
      A->>V: VLM check (bounded rate)
      V-->>A: state classification
    end

    A->>M: update derived metrics only
  end
